[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A care coordination assistant decomposes into ten logical stages: enrollment and consent, cross-organizational longitudinal-store initialization, channel entry with disclosure refresh, input safety screening with continuous emergency screening, identity-and-context loading from cross-organizational sources, conversation handling with longitudinal-store-grounded responses, output safety screening with scope verification and source-confidence stamping, action-on-behalf-of-patient routing with policy enforcement, care-team reporting with consent enforcement, and audit logging with multi-stakeholder retention discipline. The cross-cutting concerns from recipes 11.1 through 11.8 carry forward; this recipe adds five new ones (cross-organizational data integration with identity resolution, referral-and-prior-auth-and-transition state-machine engines, patient-advocacy-voice discipline, action-on-behalf-of-patient policy with explicit scope, and multi-stakeholder audit posture).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ENROLLMENT + CONSENT ──────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient enrolls via care team referral, payer          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    enrollment, employer benefits, or self-enrollment]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Documented consent specific to coordination,         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      reviewed by legal counsel and clinical leadership    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Coordination-tool nature disclosure acknowledged     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cross-organizational data-source consent             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (which sources to pull from)                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team sharing consent (which destinations to     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      push to)                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Act-on-behalf-of-patient consent scope (which        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      actions the coordinator may take without explicit    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      patient confirmation per interaction)                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - State-specific consent variations enforced           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: signed consent record; enrollment              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    confirmation; initialization of longitudinal store]    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── CROSS-ORG LONGITUDINAL STORE INITIALIZATION ───┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient identity resolution across organizations]      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Match patient across consented data sources          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Resolve MRN-to-MRN linkages                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Establish canonical identity for the coordinator     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Coordinator longitudinal store]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Provider-and-organization roster                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active conditions on the problem list across orgs    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Reconciled medication list across pharmacies and     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      prescribers                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scheduled appointments across providers              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Open referrals with lifecycle stage                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pending prior authorizations with lifecycle stage    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent encounter summaries across organizations      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Open clinical loops (lab follow-up, imaging          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      follow-up, specialist follow-up, recommended-but-    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      not-scheduled)                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent transitions of care                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Billing and coverage events                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation history                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Storage architecture]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Structured data: DynamoDB tables                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation transcript: S3 with vector retrieval    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cross-organizational source registry: which orgs,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      which feeds, which freshness, which last-pull        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: longitudinal store ready for coordination      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    conversations]                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── CHANNEL ENTRY WITH DISCLOSURE ─────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-initiated entry]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - In-app chat (most common)                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    273[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - SMS (where supported)                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    274[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Web chat                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    275[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Voice channel (where supported, with accessibility)  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    276[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    277[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Coordinator-initiated entry]                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    278[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Lifecycle-event-triggered (referral approaching      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      expiration, prior auth pending too long, transition  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    280[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      of care follow-up needed)                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    281[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scheduled check-ins per care plan                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    282[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Medication-reconciliation prompts after detected     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    283[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      discrepancies                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team-requested patient outreach                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    285[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    286[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Disclosure refresh per session or per defined cadence] │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    287[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "I'm a coordination tool, not a person"              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    288[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "I help with logistics, not clinical decisions"      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "If you have an urgent symptom, here's how to reach  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      a clinician"                                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient acknowledges or continues                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    292[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    293[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    294[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: session_id, channel, auth context, disclosure  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    295[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    acknowledged]                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    296[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    297[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    298[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    299[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── INPUT SAFETY + EMERGENCY SCREENING ────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    300[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    301[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Standard input safety primitives from recipe 11.1]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    302[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prompt-injection detection                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    303[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - PHI minimization                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    304[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    305[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Continuous emergency screening (from recipes 11.6      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    306[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    and 11.8)]                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    307[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Acute-symptom screening (chest pain, stroke          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    308[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      symptoms, severe shortness of breath, severe         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    309[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      bleeding, anaphylaxis, severe abdominal pain,        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    310[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      severe head injury, etc.)                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    311[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis screening (suicidal ideation, self-harm,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    312[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      homicidal ideation)                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    313[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Mandatory-reporting screening (child abuse, elder    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    314[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      abuse, intimate-partner violence)                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    315[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Triggers acute pathway immediately on positive       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    316[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      screen, regardless of conversation state             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    317[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    318[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Sensitive-disclosure detection]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    319[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Severe medication side effects                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    320[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Medication-discontinuation disclosures               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    321[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Substance-use crisis indicators                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    322[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Adverse-care experiences (medical-error              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    323[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      disclosures, patient-safety concerns)                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    324[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    325[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    326[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: input passes / input blocked / acute pathway   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    327[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    triggered / sensitive disclosure flagged for routing]  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    328[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    329[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    330[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    331[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── IDENTITY + CROSS-ORG CONTEXT LOADING ──────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    332[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    333[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Authenticated session]                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    334[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient is logged into the institution's app or      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    335[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      portal                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    336[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Session conveys verified patient_id and access scope │
